1. `code-bug / HIGH` 前端仍按 exam-ai 旧角色做权限判定，和后端当前返回的 canonical 角色不一致，多个主流程会直接错显或隐藏。后端登录明确返回 `platform_admin` / `homeroom_teacher` / `subject_teacher` 等角色，[auth.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/auth.py#L46)；前端登录也原样保存该角色，[auth.js](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/stores/auth.js#L16)。但导航和管理页仍只识别 `admin/teacher/head_teacher/subject_leader`，并且引用了 store 中根本不存在的 `auth.isAdmin`，[AppNavbar.vue](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/AppNavbar.vue#L20) [AppNavbar.vue](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/AppNavbar.vue#L43) [AppNavbar.vue](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/AppNavbar.vue#L48) [AppNavbar.vue](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/AppNavbar.vue#L76)。`MarkingAssignPage` 也只把 `admin/principal` 视为管理者，[MarkingAssignPage.vue](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/MarkingAssignPage.vue#L84)。结果是 `platform_admin`、`academic_director`、`homeroom_teacher`、`subject_teacher` 登录后菜单和页面权限都会错。

2. `code-bug / MED` AI 健康检查前后端契约不一致，前端会把健康的 AI 服务判成不可用。后端 `/api/v1/ai/health` 返回 `{"status":"ok"}`，[ai.py](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/api/ai.py#L56)；前端 `checkHealth()` 只接受 `"available"`，[aiChat.js](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/stores/aiChat.js#L17) [aiChat.js](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/stores/aiChat.js#L21)。这会让 `isAvailable` 永远是 `false`。

